&lt;li&gt;Build reliable, incremental pipelines that support deduplication, late-arriving data, watermarking, reprocessing, and reproducible aggregations at scale.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Model context and relationships across machines, lines, factories, sensors, work orders, and tenants to support structured queries and AI-driven experiences.&lt;/li&gt;
