&lt;li&gt;Define and enforce data modeling standards (raw / modeled / aggregate layers, e.g., Bronze/Silver/Gold) across DIH systems.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Make key architectural decisions across storage, lakehouse, and streaming systems (e.g., Databricks, Kafka), including trade-offs in cost, latency, and correctness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead design reviews and guide engineers through complex distributed systems and data pipeline decisions.&lt;/li&gt;
